  "detailed_description": "<strong>WARNING</strong>: <i>This game contains flashing images that some users may find uncomfortable. <br>It may not be suitable for people with photosensitive epilepsy. Please be advised before playing.</i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Info:</h2><strong>Block Wizard</strong> is an<strong> arcade puzzle</strong> game that aims to challenge both your <strong>wits </strong>and <strong>speed</strong>!<br><br>As you awaken inside the <strong>fiendish </strong>labyrinth, the only goal in sight is a flight of stairs.<br><br><i>What awaits on the other side?</i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Race through each one of the <strong>100 floors</strong>, and climb to the top, avoiding the nightmares in your way.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Change between a retro look or modern pixel art!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1434300/extras/2b426deb39dd92b156bacab0eef19e7d.poster.avif?t=1612304507\" width=282 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1434300/extras/2b426deb39dd92b156bacab0eef19e7d.webm?t=1612304507\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1434300/extras/2b426deb39dd92b156bacab0eef19e7d.mp4?t=1612304507\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Solve challenging puzzles using your unique ability to modify the environment at will with your magic!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1434300/extras/380d116010dcbe4977baf08ded03cadf.poster.avif?t=1612304507\" width=260 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1434300/extras/380d116010dcbe4977baf08ded03cadf.webm?t=1612304507\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1434300/extras/380d116010dcbe4977baf08ded03cadf.mp4?t=1612304507\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Play using responsive controls requiring <strong>precision</strong> and <strong>speed</strong>! </li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1434300/extras/51b36e32b54f8b446b11b86f7f456585.poster.avif?t=1612304507\" width=274 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1434300/extras/51b36e32b54f8b446b11b86f7f456585.webm?t=1612304507\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1434300/extras/51b36e32b54f8b446b11b86f7f456585.mp4?t=1612304507\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Use the in-game clock to beat your own scores!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1434300/extras/522d05acbc3c4dd66e3bd094bcbfc408.poster.avif?t=1612304507\" width=282 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1434300/extras/522d05acbc3c4dd66e3bd094bcbfc408.webm?t=1612304507\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1434300/extras/522d05acbc3c4dd66e3bd094bcbfc408.mp4?t=1612304507\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i>What's the fastest you can climb?</i><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DEMO FEATURES</h2></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Experience the <strong>first 20 levels</strong></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Carry over</strong> your progress to the full game!</li></ul><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FULL GAME</h2></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Unlock all <strong>100</strong> levels!</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Save your <strong>highscore</strong> on the <strong>leaderboards</strong>!</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Use <strong>Level Select</strong> to practice any stage you want!</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Set the <strong>best</strong> score for <strong>each Wing</strong> and top the <strong>leaderboards</strong>!</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Use <strong>CHAOS mode</strong> to face every floor in a randomized order for a true test of skill. Pickups from previous levels do<strong> NOT</strong> carry over.</li></ul><br><i>Are you the real Block Wizard?</i>",
